{"an8.15:0.1":"Anguttara Nikaya 8.15 ","an8.15:0.2":"2. Mahavagga ","an8.15:0.3":"Malasutta ","an8.15:1.1":"“Atthimani, bhikkhave, malani. ","an8.15:1.2":"Katamani attha? ","an8.15:1.3":"Asajjhayamala, bhikkhave, manta; ","an8.15:1.4":"anutthanamala, bhikkhave, ghara; ","an8.15:1.5":"malam, bhikkhave, vannassa kosajjam; ","an8.15:1.6":"pamado, bhikkhave, rakkhato malam; ","an8.15:1.7":"malam, bhikkhave, itthiya duccaritam; ","an8.15:1.8":"maccheram, bhikkhave, dadato malam; ","an8.15:1.9":"mala, bhikkhave, papaka akusala dhamma asmim loke paramhi ca; ","an8.15:1.10":"tato, bhikkhave, mala malataram avijja paramam malam. ","an8.15:1.11":"Imani kho, bhikkhave, attha malaniti. ","an8.15:2.1":"Asajjhayamala manta, ","an8.15:2.2":"anutthanamala ghara; ","an8.15:2.3":"Malam vannassa kosajjam, ","an8.15:2.4":"pamado rakkhato malam. ","an8.15:3.1":"Malitthiya duccaritam, ","an8.15:3.2":"maccheram dadato malam; ","an8.15:3.3":"Mala ve papaka dhamma, ","an8.15:3.4":"asmim loke paramhi ca; ","an8.15:3.5":"Tato mala malataram, ","an8.15:3.6":"avijja paramam malan”ti. ","an8.15:3.7":"Pancamam. "}